  The strongest finding: the UNIVERSAL MODULUS 8R₂ appears
  in five of six domains as the phase period, and R₂ is present
  in all six. The Maslov-Berry connection (Q1) and the
  theta-BZ connection (Q6) are both exact identities that
  become tautological when expressed in R₂ units.

  This points toward Phase 3 outcome (b): PARTIAL COLLAPSE.
  Five 'phase-periodic' domains share modulus 8R₂.
  Chern-Simons has modulus 1 (topological, not geometric).
  The VP running shares R₂ but lacks periodicity.
  